{"tid":2366146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[地主又贏] 高等法院上訴庭周三裁定政府及鄉議局勝訴，即丁屋政策完全沒有違憲","createTime":"2021-01-14T09:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T10:43:23.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea13fdaab4432d6667ca35466dbecea5b1cb1a7e","tid":2366146,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"高等法院於前年就丁權司法覆核案裁定，以私人協約或換地形式建丁屋違憲，其後涉案三方就裁決上訴。高等法院上訴庭周三（13日）裁定政府及鄉議局勝訴，即丁屋政策完全沒有違憲。<br />\n<br />\n提出司法覆核的郭卓堅稱，會就案件上訴至終審法院，但承認現今「政治氣候」之下，「輸嘅機會多。」但他強調「唔可以唔出聲。」並反駁上訴庭的說法指自己並非事關政策的「持份者」，重申全港市民都是丁屋政策的持份者。<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社則指，上訴庭未有處理政策歧視女性及非原居民的問題，亦無考慮港人於丁屋政策被濫用所受的損害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426107975409602560890431.jpeg/NW7gEer0nEKDWgwc7jtXM_ceA8rEI9t7LfXvki3175I?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426107975409602560890431.jpeg%2FNW7gEer0nEKDWgwc7jtXM_ceA8rEI9t7LfXvki3175I%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=02686c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n判辭：丁權為「長久被認可及合法｣<br />\n<br />\n上訴案由首席法官潘兆初、上訴庭副庭長林文瀚及上訴庭法官區慶祥審理。判辭中提到，丁權於1898年前推行的傳統，即使於其後土地的用途有所改變，仍被法例等保障及視為合法，「亦未受挑戰或被視為不合法」。判詞指，丁權為「長久被認可及合法｣（They had all along been recognized and accepted to be lawful.）。判詞亦提到，於1990年草擬《基本法》時已考慮丁屋政策屬合法的傳統權益。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭又指出，原審法官指換地及私人協約批地形式建屋沒有可追溯歷史為錯誤，認為兩個方式為慣有的土地使用制度（customary tenure）。<br />\n<br />\n引國際歧視公約 指丁屋獲豁免<br />\n<br />\n至於提出司法覆核的一方指丁權歧視女性同非原居民，與《香港人權法案條例》相違背。上訴庭於判詞中指，英國及中國政府有份簽署的國際公約《消除對婦女一切形式歧視公約》，兩國分別就丁屋政策提出豁免。上訴庭的判辭提到，制定《基本法》第40條時亦考慮到有關對歧視的豁免，以保障丁權於丁屋政策中的合法傳統權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n批提出司法覆核「異常地延誤」<br />\n<br />\n此外，判辭中指丁屋政策於1972年頒布，而《香港人權法案條例》則於1991年通過，而基本法則生效23年。上訴庭指，提出司法覆核的時期不僅是「嚴重延誤」（not only serious），而是「異常地延誤」（phenomenal）。判詞指，案件對可享用丁屋政策的原居民構成影響，亦對新界土地政策構成影響。上訴庭又認為，提出司法覆核的一方於丁屋政策上「無利害關係」。（they do not have any interest over and above that of an ordinary resident which give them standing to bring the judicial review.）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065598573711360825637.jpeg/nWU_fUIFU8jJhkdRz1_EYkI4-a1N8bb9h03qk4dN6pM?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065598573711360825637.jpeg%2FnWU_fUIFU8jJhkdRz1_EYkI4-a1N8bb9h03qk4dN6pM%3Fv%3Dw640&h=a59b708d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065601681821696419730.jpeg/31-Tx04q3L5bX6AAIear6OQIc-I5hamklS_A4pUvwOI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065601681821696419730.jpeg%2F31-Tx04q3L5bX6AAIear6OQIc-I5hamklS_A4pUvwOI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3aedde30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065604185952256496273.jpeg/8BGkdyuwoOYS5gmtfKwEsdOO3btBvj3xERii5BEYouQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065604185952256496273.jpeg%2F8BGkdyuwoOYS5gmtfKwEsdOO3btBvj3xERii5BEYouQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1f0cb0b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065606300012544850746.jpeg/1lzfxOgBKK5OrqvSEp8I4lCeaOeOP1pnOHUDejh1A3o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065606300012544850746.jpeg%2F1lzfxOgBKK5OrqvSEp8I4lCeaOeOP1pnOHUDejh1A3o%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=124b28f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065608875446272354720.jpeg/Q5xNi-2xFH0AoJVvob48qu-Avq7VxBzk0xAon9MQKJ8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065608875446272354720.jpeg%2FQ5xNi-2xFH0AoJVvob48qu-Avq7VxBzk0xAon9MQKJ8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e9d201ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065611220193280307652.jpeg/vcsyud8R5_M2djmNMJX9_ovatzzDfICYUpc2AFKXNgA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065611220193280307652.jpeg%2Fvcsyud8R5_M2djmNMJX9_ovatzzDfICYUpc2AFKXNgA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ab216dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065613401362432725049.jpeg/cFaegI1lUqGXuAJ3vreHYj91dFdJmtLBmn5tjZp-bY0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065613401362432725049.jpeg%2FcFaegI1lUqGXuAJ3vreHYj91dFdJmtLBmn5tjZp-bY0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=30df49af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065615850967040256341.jpeg/kajPOII2aGy40EEKwT2ep7FPrf0b2IYA6mIFBepiBQU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065615850967040256341.jpeg%2FkajPOII2aGy40EEKwT2ep7FPrf0b2IYA6mIFBepiBQU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=97094f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065618237657088273984.jpeg/2lx2dy_mXBAAiQfzmMzFMYbEydXsDMNGcqj7ZHKo-2Q?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065618237657088273984.jpeg%2F2lx2dy_mXBAAiQfzmMzFMYbEydXsDMNGcqj7ZHKo-2Q%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=83772db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065620737593344401652.jpeg/Gf_VpMspkKJqTj2Th-Pgf980akzQYdFxyvtA0cr7QNE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065620737593344401652.jpeg%2FGf_VpMspkKJqTj2Th-Pgf980akzQYdFxyvtA0cr7QNE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=bf5c6565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065590910717952496825.jpeg/Z3-oggRUoqjKVAv23mUnPdan5nv00Tc0UvMKM1LzCjM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065590910717952496825.jpeg%2FZ3-oggRUoqjKVAv23mUnPdan5nv00Tc0UvMKM1LzCjM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=87a10a7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210113/426065593372905472687913.jpeg/SN1lSbOjsh0Lo0te87dKgbFXwASOuMtAq7iJ9qu4ifY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210113%2F426065593372905472687913.jpeg%2FSN1lSbOjsh0Lo0te87dKgbFXwASOuMtAq7iJ9qu4ifY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f07fecfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本研社：提司法覆核時間與條例生效日期不應有關連<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社成員黃肇鴻表示，上訴庭的判詞有不少值得商榷的地方，如未有正面處理歧視女性同非原居民的問題，就算90年代通過的《香港人權法案條例》有考慮對丁屋政策的豁免，隨著社會變化，有關政策是否有改善空間。他指，國際有案例容許歧視存在，但需要考慮其必要性及是否合乎比例，但法庭於今次案件未有著墨。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，看不到換地及私人協約批地形式的可追溯性，「清朝個時都無賣地啦。」他指，上訴庭視乎將1990年草擬《基本法》的委員會視為「大晒」，認為若當年草委當年一致認為丁屋屬傳統權益，應將其寫入條文，指法庭認為草委一致認為丁屋屬傳統權益的說法值得商榷。他又指，過往亦有取消傳統權益的案例，如70年代廢除納妾，認為提出司法覆核與條例生效時期無關，又指上訴庭未有看到全港市民於政策上受害。"},{"pid":"ace4c77d5b80f3fc8f63289d6cc1dd1257fff9bd","tid":2366146,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">上訴案由首席法官潘兆初、上訴庭副庭長林文瀚及上訴庭法官區慶祥</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af845f2dc2eea3bca242882597a7693a06afb0e8","tid":2366146,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"要求人大釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e95d4d76d7cb4b1ace8b36352d2b8f7a3c549a","tid":2366146,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MT6fyEX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMT6fyEX.jpg&h=3121a163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3666002eab60a5556576995423b7a0cacb153b5","tid":2366146,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHccvhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHccvhq.jpg&h=d2fe5dc3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}